                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7295" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1135</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9076 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">lululemon——顾客的教育家</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">lululemon—The Customer’ s Educator</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘欣，桑辉，杜雨清，岳冰菁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海对外经贸大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">露露柠檬（Lululemon Athletica Inc.)</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客教育；露露乐蒙；品牌社区营销；内部营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Customer Education; lululemon; Brand Community Marketing；Internal Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例展现了露露乐蒙建立的一个由品牌大使、教育家、门店活动和消费者构建的品牌社群营销体系以及顾客教育在其中国市场发展中所起到的重要作用和面临的挑战。创立于1998年的露露乐蒙公司，以一条黑色女性瑜伽裤打入运动休闲市场，凭借其独特的营销方式迅速获得了消费者的热烈追捧，缔造了品牌增长的奇迹。自2013年进入中国以来，露露乐蒙公司延续了原有的营销方式，在顾客教育家的工作开展下，销售业绩抢眼，门店扩张迅速。然而，扩张后如何招募深谙品牌价值观及产品特性的顾客教育家？如何确保每家门店教育家提供的服务质量保持统一？如何更好地教育中国消费者？这些成为露露乐蒙（中国）管理者亟待解决的棘手问题。本案例旨在帮助学员加深对品牌社群营销以及顾客教育的理解，明确露露乐蒙开展顾客教育的原因和方法，了解其在品牌迅速扩张过程中招募、培养和管理顾客教育家的实施要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes lululemon &#39;s brand community marketing system, which is built by brand ambassadors, educators, store activities and consumers, and the important role of customer education in the development of its Chinese market and the challenges it faces. lululemon, founded in 1998, broke into the sports leisure market with a black yoga pants for women. With its unique marketing approach, it quickly won the enthusiastic pursuit of consumers and created a miracle of brand growth. Since entering China in 2013, lululemon has continued its original marketing approach. Thanks to the work of customer educators, lululemon has achieved impressive sales performance and rapid store expansion. However, how to recruit customer educators who understand brand values and product characteristics after expansion? How to ensure that the quality of service provided by educators in each store remains uniform? How to educate Chinese customers more effectively? These are the thorny problems that lululemon Chinese managers need to solve. This case aims to help students deepen their understanding of brand community marketing and customer education, clarify the reasons and methods for lululemon to carry out customer education, and understand the key points of implementation on recruiting, cultivating, and managing customer educators in the process of rapid brand expansion.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《服务营销学》、《市场营销学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客教育理论；品牌社群营销理论；关系营销理论；5W模型；内部营销理论；服务营销三角形模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
